review_reply.reply_text: Hi Gud evening. The best treatment for a toe fracture is a plaster for 3 to 4 weeks. Otherwise there tend to be some persistent pain and some displacement of the fracture. Regarding the removal treatment protocols differ from doctor to doctor and putting a plaster always does good rather than harm to a patient.
